{
  "video_id": "RCXGpEmFbOw",
  "title": "Meet the dazzling flying machines of the future | Raffaello D'Andrea",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12920.0,
      "end_time": 14896.0,
      "text": "What started as a platform for hobbyists"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14920.0,
      "end_time": 17856.0,
      "text": "is poised to become a multibillion-dollar industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17880.0,
      "end_time": 21936.0,
      "text": "Inspection, environmental monitoring, photography and film and journalism:"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21960.0,
      "end_time": 25136.0,
      "text": "these are some of the potential applications for commercial drones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25160.0,
      "end_time": 27776.0,
      "text": "and their enablers are the capabilities being developed"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27800.0,
      "end_time": 29736.0,
      "text": "at research facilities around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29760.0,
      "end_time": 32376.0,
      "text": "For example, before aerial package delivery"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32400.0,
      "end_time": 34216.0,
      "text": "entered our social consciousness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34240.0,
      "end_time": 38216.0,
      "text": "an autonomous fleet of flying machines built a six-meter-tall tower"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38240.0,
      "end_time": 40176.0,
      "text": "composed of 1,500 bricks"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40200.0,
      "end_time": 43136.0,
      "text": "in front of a live audience at the FRAC Centre in France,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43160.0,
      "end_time": 45736.0,
      "text": "and several years ago, they started to fly with ropes."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45760.0,
      "end_time": 47175.0,
      "text": "By tethering flying machines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47200.0,
      "end_time": 50976.0,
      "text": "they can achieve high speeds and accelerations in very tight spaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51000.0,
      "end_time": 54960.0,
      "text": "They can also autonomously build tensile structures."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54120.0,
      "end_time": 56535.0,
      "text": "Skills learned include how to carry loads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56560.0,
      "end_time": 58160.0,
      "text": "how to cope with disturbances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58400.0,
      "end_time": 61135.0,
      "text": "and in general, how to interact with the physical world."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61160.0,
      "end_time": 64495.0,
      "text": "Today we want to show you some new projects that we&#39;ve been working on."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64519.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67455.0,
      "text": "Their aim is to push the boundary of what can be achieved"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 67480.0,
      "end_time": 69160.0,
      "text": "with autonomous flight."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69400.0,
      "end_time": 71496.0,
      "text": "Now, for a system to function autonomously,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71520.0,
      "end_time": 75976.0,
      "text": "it must collectively know the location of its mobile objects in space."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76000.0,
      "end_time": 77896.0,
      "text": "Back at our lab at ETH Zurich,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77920.0,
      "end_time": 80776.0,
      "text": "we often use external cameras to locate objects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80800.0,
      "end_time": 82776.0,
      "text": "which then allows us to focus our efforts"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82800.0,
      "end_time": 85456.0,
      "text": "on the rapid development of highly dynamic tasks."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85480.0,
      "end_time": 87536.0,
      "text": "For the demos you will see today, however,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 87560.0,
      "end_time": 90856.0,
      "text": "we will use new localization technology developed by Verity Studios,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90880.0,
      "end_time": 92496.0,
      "text": "a spin-off from our lab."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92520.0,
      "end_time": 94136.0,
      "text": "There are no external cameras."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94160.0,
      "end_time": 99216.0,
      "text": "Each flying machine uses onboard sensors to determine its location in space"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 99240.0,
      "end_time": 102679.0,
      "text": "and onboard computation to determine what its actions should be."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 103280.0,
      "end_time": 105456.0,
      "text": "The only external commands are high-level ones"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 105480.0,
      "end_time": 107000.0,
      "text": "such as \"take off\" and \"land.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 130560.0,
      "end_time": 132456.0,
      "text": "This is a so-called tail-sitter."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 132480.0,
      "end_time": 135935.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an aircraft that tries to have its cake and eat it."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 135960.0,
      "end_time": 139216.0,
      "text": "Like other fixed-wing aircraft, it is efficient in forward flight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 139240.0,
      "end_time": 142455.0,
      "text": "much more so than helicopters and variations thereof."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 142479.0,
      "end_time": 144896.0,
      "text": "Unlike most other fixed-wing aircraft, however,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 144920.0,
      "end_time": 146416.0,
      "text": "it is capable of hovering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 146440.0,
      "end_time": 149576.0,
      "text": "which has huge advantages for takeoff, landing"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 149600.0,
      "end_time": 150840.0,
      "text": "and general versatility."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 151480.0,
      "end_time": 153576.0,
      "text": "There is no free lunch, unfortunately."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 153600.0,
      "end_time": 155536.0,
      "text": "One of the limitations with tail-sitters"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 155560.0,
      "end_time": 158536.0,
      "text": "is that they&#39;re susceptible to disturbances such as wind gusts."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 158560.0,
      "end_time": 161256.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re developing new control architectures and algorithms"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 161280.0,
      "end_time": 162680.0,
      "text": "that address this limitation."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 170560.0,
      "end_time": 172816.0,
      "text": "The idea is for the aircraft to recover"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 172840.0,
      "end_time": 175480.0,
      "text": "no matter what state it finds itself in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 183400.0,
      "end_time": 186320.0,
      "text": "and through practice, improve its performance over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 195600.0,
      "end_time": 200000.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 202000.0,
      "end_time": 203200.0,
      "text": "OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 213480.0,
      "end_time": 214696.0,
      "text": "When doing research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 214720.0,
      "end_time": 217696.0,
      "text": "we often ask ourselves fundamental abstract questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 217720.0,
      "end_time": 220280.0,
      "text": "that try to get at the heart of a matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 221240.0,
      "end_time": 223456.0,
      "text": "For example, one such question would be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 223480.0,
      "end_time": 227495.0,
      "text": "what is the minimum number of moving parts needed for controlled flight?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 227520.0,
      "end_time": 229960.0,
      "text": "Now, there are practical reasons"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 229120.0,
      "end_time": 231736.0,
      "text": "why you may want to know the answer to such a question."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 231760.0,
      "end_time": 233160.0,
      "text": "Helicopters, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 233400.0,
      "end_time": 236896.0,
      "text": "are affectionately known as machines with a thousand moving parts"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 236920.0,
      "end_time": 239600.0,
      "text": "all conspiring to do you bodily harm."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 240640.0,
      "end_time": 242495.0,
      "text": "It turns out that decades ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 242520.0,
      "end_time": 245696.0,
      "text": "skilled pilots were able to fly remote-controlled aircraft"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 245720.0,
      "end_time": 247616.0,
      "text": "that had only two moving parts:"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 247640.0,
      "end_time": 249480.0,
      "text": "a propeller and a tail rudder."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 250000.0,
      "end_time": 253120.0,
      "text": "We recently discovered that it could be done with just one."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 253600.0,
      "end_time": 254856.0,
      "text": "This is the monospinner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 254880.0,
      "end_time": 258135.0,
      "text": "the world&#39;s mechanically simplest controllable flying machine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 258160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259936.00000000003,
      "text": "invented just a few months ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 259959.0,
      "end_time": 263960.0,
      "text": "It has only one moving part, a propeller."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 263120.0,
      "end_time": 266696.0,
      "text": "It has no flaps, no hinges, no ailerons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 266720.0,
      "end_time": 269255.0,
      "text": "no other actuators, no other control surfaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 269279.0,
      "end_time": 270560.0,
      "text": "just a simple propeller."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 271320.0,
      "end_time": 273375.0,
      "text": "Even though it&#39;s mechanically simple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 273399.0,
      "end_time": 275896.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a lot going on in its little electronic brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 275920.0,
      "end_time": 280136.0,
      "text": "to allow it to fly in a stable fashion and to move anywhere it wants in space."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 280160.0,
      "end_time": 281616.0,
      "text": "Even so, it doesn&#39;t yet have"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 281640.0,
      "end_time": 283976.0,
      "text": "the sophisticated algorithms of the tail-sitter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 284000.0,
      "end_time": 286000.0,
      "text": "which means that in order to get it to fly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 286240.0,
      "end_time": 287744.0,
      "text": "I have to throw it just right."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 288800.0,
      "end_time": 292816.0,
      "text": "And because the probability of me throwing it just right is very low,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 292840.0,
      "end_time": 294736.0,
      "text": "given everybody watching me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 294760.0,
      "end_time": 296216.0,
      "text": "what we&#39;re going to do instead"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 296240.0,
      "end_time": 298416.0,
      "text": "is show you a video that we shot last night."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 298440.0,
      "end_time": 300000.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 310320.0,
      "end_time": 313640.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 323800.0,
      "end_time": 326816.0,
      "text": "If the monospinner is an exercise in frugality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 326840.0,
      "end_time": 330296.0,
      "text": "this machine here, the omnicopter, with its eight propellers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 330320.0,
      "end_time": 332400.0,
      "text": "is an exercise in excess."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 332920.0,
      "end_time": 335560.0,
      "text": "What can you do with all this surplus?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 335800.0,
      "end_time": 337460.0,
      "text": "The thing to notice is that it is highly symmetric."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 337920.0,
      "end_time": 340776.0,
      "text": "As a result, it is ambivalent to orientation."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 340800.0,
      "end_time": 343496.0,
      "text": "This gives it an extraordinary capability."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 343520.0,
      "end_time": 345736.0,
      "text": "It can move anywhere it wants in space"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 345760.0,
      "end_time": 348496.0,
      "text": "irrespective of where it is facing"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 348520.0,
      "end_time": 350320.0,
      "text": "and even of how it is rotating."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 351400.0,
      "end_time": 352416.0,
      "text": "It has its own complexities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 352440.0,
      "end_time": 355960.0,
      "text": "mainly having to do with the interacting flows"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 355120.0,
      "end_time": 356360.0,
      "text": "from its eight propellers."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 356680.0,
      "end_time": 360536.0,
      "text": "Some of this can be modeled, while the rest can be learned on the fly."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 360560.0,
      "end_time": 361760.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take a look."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 404760.0,
      "end_time": 408520.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 412720.0,
      "end_time": 415625.0,
      "text": "If flying machines are going to enter part of our daily lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 415649.0,
      "end_time": 418126.0,
      "text": "they will need to become extremely safe and reliable."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 418760.0,
      "end_time": 420135.0,
      "text": "This machine over here"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 420160.0,
      "end_time": 423296.0,
      "text": "is actually two separate two-propeller flying machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 423320.0,
      "end_time": 425560.0,
      "text": "This one wants to spin clockwise."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 425800.0,
      "end_time": 427575.0,
      "text": "This other one wants to spin counterclockwise."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 427600.0,
      "end_time": 428936.0,
      "text": "When you put them together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 428960.0,
      "end_time": 431560.0,
      "text": "they behave like one high-performance quadrocopter."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 443640.0,
      "end_time": 445296.0,
      "text": "If anything goes wrong, however --"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 445320.0,
      "end_time": 449776.0,
      "text": "a motor fails, a propeller fails, electronics, even a battery pack --"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 449800.0,
      "end_time": 453136.0,
      "text": "the machine can still fly, albeit in a degraded fashion."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 453160.0,
      "end_time": 456680.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to demonstrate this to you now by disabling one of its halves."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 476240.0,
      "end_time": 479400.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 483320.0,
      "end_time": 484656.0,
      "text": "This last demonstration"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 484680.0,
      "end_time": 487120.0,
      "text": "is an exploration of synthetic swarms."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 487560.0,
      "end_time": 490536.0,
      "text": "The large number of autonomous, coordinated entities"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 490560.0,
      "end_time": 493296.0,
      "text": "offers a new palette for aesthetic expression."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 493320.0,
      "end_time": 496296.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve taken commercially available micro quadcopters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 496320.0,
      "end_time": 498816.0,
      "text": "each weighing less than a slice of bread, by the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 498840.0,
      "end_time": 501256.0,
      "text": "and outfitted them with our localization technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 501280.0,
      "end_time": 502856.0,
      "text": "and custom algorithms."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 502880.0,
      "end_time": 504976.0,
      "text": "Because each unit knows where it is in space"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 505000.0,
      "end_time": 506376.0,
      "text": "and is self-controlled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 506400.0,
      "end_time": 508599.0,
      "text": "there is really no limit to their number."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 535840.0,
      "end_time": 539280.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 559360.0,
      "end_time": 563840.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 618400.0,
      "end_time": 621680.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 635960.0,
      "end_time": 639560.0,
      "text": "Hopefully, these demonstrations will motivate you to dream up"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 639800.0,
      "end_time": 641480.0,
      "text": "new revolutionary roles for flying machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 642560.0,
      "end_time": 644656.0,
      "text": "That ultrasafe one over there for example"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 644680.0,
      "end_time": 647695.0,
      "text": "has aspirations to become a flying lampshade on Broadway."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 647720.0,
      "end_time": 649776.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 649800.0,
      "end_time": 651976.0,
      "text": "The reality is that it is difficult to predict"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 652000.0,
      "end_time": 653640.0,
      "text": "the impact of nascent technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 654120.0,
      "end_time": 658976.0,
      "text": "And for folks like us, the real reward is the journey and the act of creation."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 659000.0,
      "end_time": 660416.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a continual reminder"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 660440.0,
      "end_time": 663360.0,
      "text": "of how wonderful and magical the universe we live in is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 663840.0,
      "end_time": 666776.0,
      "text": "that it allows creative, clever creatures"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 666800.0,
      "end_time": 669319.0,
      "text": "to sculpt it in such spectacular ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 669800.0,
      "end_time": 671575.0,
      "text": "The fact that this technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 671600.0,
      "end_time": 675160.0,
      "text": "has such huge commercial and economic potential"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 675400.0,
      "end_time": 676456.0,
      "text": "is just icing on the cake."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 676480.0,
      "end_time": 677696.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 677720.0,
      "end_time": 680960.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}